# Botfeed project structure

Monorepo with four apps (directory names are historical):

| Directory | Stack | Purpose |
|-----------|-------|---------|
| `Wapi-frontend/` | Next.js 14 (App Router), RTK Query, Tailwind, i18n | User-facing SaaS dashboard |
| `Wapi-admin/` | Next.js, Tailwind | Admin panel |
| `wapi-api/` | Express, Mongoose, Socket.IO | REST API + WebSocket server |
| `wapi-documentation/` | Static HTML | API documentation site |

## Frontend key paths

- Pages: `Wapi-frontend/src/app/(mainLayout)/`
- Components: `Wapi-frontend/src/components/`
- API layer: `Wapi-frontend/src/redux/api/` (RTK Query)
- Locales: `Wapi-frontend/src/locales/{en,ar,es}/translation.json`
- Guards: `Wapi-frontend/src/shared/` (RoleGuard, FeatureGuard, SubscriptionGuard)

## Backend key paths

- Routes: `wapi-api/routes/`
- Controllers: `wapi-api/controllers/`
- Models: `wapi-api/models/`
- Middleware: `wapi-api/middlewares/`
- Config: `wapi-api/.env`

## Conventions

- Backend runs on port 5001 (`wapi-api/server.js`)
- Frontend dev server on port 3000
- MongoDB via Mongoose; Redis for queues
- i18n: `useTranslation()` + flat key structure (`sidebar.dashboard`, `common.save`)
